00:32:52.458 --> 00:32:56.338
tumor-CAF crosstalk. So this is kind of a

572
00:32:56.398 --> 00:32:57.238
summary of our model.

573
00:32:58.058 --> 00:32:59.418
We started by collecting

574
00:33:00.278 --> 00:33:03.698
EpCAM positive urothelial cells, these are the cells that line the inside of the

575
00:33:03.718 --> 00:33:07.698
bladder, from this special transgenic mouse that was described in

576
00:33:07.818 --> 00:33:10.438
2014 by the Fung Zhong group.

