00:34:41.078 --> 00:34:44.859
E545K mutation. The problem we ran

604
00:34:44.899 --> 00:34:48.798
into is there's not really a good PAM site for our CRISPR enzyme

605
00:34:49.879 --> 00:34:52.158
that's close to E545K, but we're actually really

