00:34:53.198 --> 00:34:56.419
easily able to make the 1047 mutation.

607
00:34:56.919 --> 00:35:00.278
We used a molecular trick that's described by Kan et al. in 2017.

608
00:35:02.018 --> 00:35:02.638
So once we

609
00:35:03.598 --> 00:35:06.338
generated these hotspot mutations, we

